    "body": "I think that we need to provide as faithful bindings as possible to the actual api functions, and the signature is indeed this:\n\n``` c\nchar * strerror(int errnum);\n```\n\nIn light of that, I'm going to close this. So far we haven't deviated from the actual definitions themselves, and its unknown if we may want to consider doing so for one-off cases such as this.\n",
